    "text": "@flightofthefox this one is for you\n\n**Subintents are coming to TypeScript in **`**@radix****-effects/tx-tool@0.1.0-dev.0**`\nI've shipped early Subintent support in `@radix-effects/tx-tool`, and I'm looking for builders to test it in real workflows.\n\nTry it now:\n`pnpm add ```@radix-effects/tx-tool@0.1.0-dev.0``\n\nI'm especially looking for feedback on:\n• Multi-party / partial signing flows\n• Composable transaction pipelines\n• DX rough edges, confusing APIs, or missing examples\n• Bugs or unexpected behavior in real dApps\n\nExample code:\nhttps://github.com/xstelea/radix-web3.js/blob/subintent/packages/tx-tool/src/createTransactionIntent.spec.ts#L119-L364\n\nThis is a dev prerelease, so now is the best time to shape the stable release.\nLet me know if you get any issues.",
