    "text": "through scrypto, use `.set_role` on your locker component:\n```pub fn set_role(&self, role: String, new_rule: AccessRule) {\n            self.locker.set_role(&role, new_rule);\n}```\n\nthrough manifest, use the `SET_ROLE` instruction, example:\n```SET_ROLE\n  Address(\"locker_rdx1drrfl4phkx3jr5pf8klule39le4gzw0nr4khrex3sxfl7rw2h4yckk\")\n  Enum<0u8>()\n  \"storer\"\n  Enum<2u8>(\n    Enum<0u8>(\n      Enum<0u8>(\n        Enum<1u8>(\n          Address(\"resource_rdx1tknxxxxxxxxxradxrdxxxxxxxxx009923554798xxxxxxxxxradxrd\")\n        )\n      )\n    )\n  )\n;```",
