    "id": 63653,
    "text": "Rejected before signing, when generating the TX preview:\n```{\n    \"ok\": false,\n    \"error\": \"failedToPrepareTransaction\",\n    \"message\": \"Error when generating TX preview: Unknown account.\"\n}```\n\n\nFor reference, here is the rejected manifest. The account ending in 0e5f is managed by my wallet. The account ending in 9gsl is not managed by any wallet. It is controlled by a badge that must first be produced from my wallet managed account:\n```CALL_METHOD\n    Address(\"account_tdx_2…0e5f\")\n    \"withdraw_non_fungibles\"\n    Address(\"resource_tdx_2…7prv\")\n    Array<NonFungibleLocalId>(\n        NonFungibleLocalId(\"<mike>\")\n    )\n;\nTAKE_NON_FUNGIBLES_FROM_WORKTOP\n    Address(\"resource_tdx_2…7prv\")\n    Array<NonFungibleLocalId>(\n        NonFungibleLocalId(\"<mike>\")\n    )\n    Bucket(\"bucket1\")\n;\nCREATE_PROOF_FROM_BUCKET_OF_ALL\n    Bucket(\"bucket1\")\n    Proof(\"proof1\")\n;\nPUSH_TO_AUTH_ZONE\n    Proof(\"proof1\")\n;\nCALL_METHOD\n    Address(\"account_tdx_2…9gsl\")\n    \"create_proof_of_non_fungibles\"\n    Address(\"resource_tdx_2…4k38\")\n    Array<NonFungibleLocalId>(\n        NonFungibleLocalId(\"<burn_resource__0792f12fc6f04990745037ea2683ffc3>\")\n    )\n;\nPOP_FROM_AUTH_ZONE\n    Proof(\"proof2\")\n;\nCALL_METHOD\n    Address(\"component_tdx_2…7xh4z\")\n    \"update_form\"\n    Proof(\"proof2\")\n    Tuple(\n        Enum<0u8>(),\n        Enum<0u8>()\n    )\n    Enum<0u8>()\n;\nPOP_FROM_AUTH_ZONE\n    Proof(\"proof3\")\n;\nDROP_PROOF\n    Proof(\"proof3\")\n;\nCALL_METHOD\n    Address(\"account_tdx_2…0e5f\")\n    \"deposit\"\n    Bucket(\"bucket1\")\n;```",
    "date": "2026-01-21T13:41:06.000Z",
    "sender": "6008290380",
    "senderName": "Mark - Radix Forms | The Radix Billboard",
    "hasMedia": false,
    "mediaType": null,
    "replyTo": 63652
