  {
    "id": 63605,
    "text": "**Wakeup babe a new P2P trustless lend / borrow dapp using sub-intents just dropped!!**\n\nMarco \"the Maestro\" Michelino and I are proud to announce the testnet launch of a new p2p Lending dApp. Working with Marco on the Smart Contract development and myself on the backend and front end we are releasing Blend ( a working title for now) that allows users to submit lend or borrow requests using three core assets. XRD, xUSDC and LSULPs. We'd love for you guys to come and test it out on Stokenet.\n\nIt should be fairly straight forward to navigate. \n\n**The key features are**\n- Create Lend offers with configurable parameters like maturity date, duration, etc\n- Create Borrow offers and choose preferred collateral of XRD, LSULP or xUSDC\n- Two way auto-matching of Lend and Borrow orders. ie. If someone submits a Lend offer and someone submits a borrow offer that matches the Lend parameters, the transaction will auto execute.\n- Liquidation page that allows both lender liquidation or 3rd party liquidations (3rd party liquidations using Astrolescent DEX swaps are not available on Stokenet)\n- Lot's of cool UI features and info to keep track of loans and monitor their health.\n\nIf you'd like to give it a whirl then you can test it out here https://blend-stokenet.fly.dev/\n\n**Feedback and questions in the Blend Test TG group please**\nhttps://t.me/blendtest",
    "date": "2026-01-13T21:25:39.000Z",
    "sender": "316385590",
    "senderName": "avaunt > ShardSpace | Notix | Atomix | Bullring",
    "hasMedia": true,
    "mediaType": "MessageMediaWebPage",
    "replyTo": null
  },
