    "id": 63010,
    "text": "Can someone enlighten me about the dapp definition model please.\n\nI don’t get why it’s managed through an account that has to be set up for this.\n\nWouldn’t it be much simpler and more robust if dapp definition where a type that is tied to component, so every main dapp component to have a „manage dapp definition“ method.\n\nThis can use the role based Auth system for flexible admin rights etc.\n\nThe account based model we have now makes dapps more insecure, because if any seedphrase may get leaked there is no easy way to switch the dapp definition account to another.\n\nA Owner / Admin badge on the other hand can be easily transferred to a safe account.\n\nHappy to learn Ugh",
