  {
    "id": 62955,
    "text": "Some time ago I got that to work to get a private key for a babylon wallet created via app: \n\n```const { MnemonicPhrase, Path } = require('@code-wallet/mnemonic')\n\nfunction PrivateKeyRawEntropy_Get(_accountName){ \n  const mnemonic = new MnemonicPhrase(gAccounts[_accountName].mnemonic)\n  const path = new Path(gAccounts[_accountName].path.replaceAll('H',\"'\"));\n  const keypair = mnemonic.toKeypair(path)\n  return keypair.privateKey\n}\n\n//THEN ...\nconst lPKEntropy = PrivateKeyRawEntropy_Get(liAccountName)\nconst lePrivateKey = new PrivateKey.Ed25519(lPKEntropy) //PrivateKey from @radixdlt/radix-engine-toolkit```\n\nSomebody has something similar that can be used with olympia account?",
    "date": "2025-11-17T12:58:51.000Z",
