    "id": 62909,
    "text": "Happy to say the problem has now been fixed. It turned out to be simple issue, I was mistaking the initial publickKey value of ’01’ as the ed25519 key type indicator but then realised it juyst happens that the public key value is starting with ’01’ because stripping this out reduced the key length to 31 bytes which couldn’t be right.\n\n1] [ROLA-SIG-DEBUG] ========== SIGNATURE VERIFICATION DETAILS ==========\n[1] [ROLA-SIG-DEBUG] Challenge: 91a040c45f41c885b5320882c3725fb303b3e4d69e7f6b54166969777e1a512d\n[1] [ROLA-SIG-DEBUG] Public Key: 0116cdf4eb55eb071da45725718cec4962d75720e5a4b0a409d5971a287a3bc4\n[1] [ROLA-SIG-DEBUG] Signature: b5818fae7ca7b672eb598621d7a6b861b0e49de4a6489d13330f93348ec29032e04ebb02d7bfc6d5db4f955d2e6689e01f6639564066d3851ea43ab875505a04\n[1] [ROLA-SIG-DEBUG] Curve: curve25519\n[1] [ROLA-SIG-DEBUG] Challenge (hex): 91a040c45f41c885b5320882c3725fb303b3e4d69e7f6b54166969777e1a512d\n[1] [ROLA-SIG-DEBUG] Message buffer length: 124 bytes\n[1] [ROLA-SIG-DEBUG] Message buffer (hex): 5291a040c45f41c885b5320882c3725fb303b3e4d69e7f6b54166969777e1a512d456163636f756e745f7464785f325f3132386e37736d766c6766306875646d3570356136376d397461727533306e7a337871786e367366377378747a68303073776b796e366c687474703a2f2f6c6f63616c686f73743a35313733\n[1] [ROLA-SIG-DEBUG] BLAKE2B hash: 65565fe79694e6cf77acca0b13bf0fc63851f8cbb892505c1ae72551581142bb\n[1] [ROLA-SIG-DEBUG] Using Ed25519 verification...\n[1] [ROLA-SIG-DEBUG] Public key (original): 0116cdf4eb55eb071da45725718cec4962d75720e5a4b0a409d5971a287a3bc4\n[1] [ROLA-SIG-DEBUG] Public key (for verification): 0116cdf4eb55eb071da45725718cec4962d75720e5a4b0a409d5971a287a3bc4\n[1] [ROLA-SIG-DEBUG] Public key length: 64 chars (should be 64)\n[1] [ROLA-SIG-DEBUG] Signature length: 128 chars (should be 128)\n[1] [ROLA-SIG-DEBUG] Message hash (to verify against): 65565fe79694e6cf77acca0b13bf0fc63851f8cbb892505c1ae72551581142bb\n[1] [ROLA-SIG-DEBUG] Signature (to verify): b5818fae7ca7b672eb598621d7a6b861b0e49de4a6489d13330f93348ec29032e04ebb02d7bfc6d5db4f955d2e6689e01f6639564066d3851ea43ab875505a04\n[1] [ROLA-SIG-DEBUG] Verification result: true\n[1] [ROLA-SIMPLE] ✅ Signature cryptographically valid\n[1] [ROLA-SIMPLE] ℹ️  ROLA authentication successful\n[1] [ROLA-SIMPLE] ℹ️  Badge authorization will be checked separately by client\n[1] [ROLA-Session] Created for: account_tdx_2_12y85k...\n[1] [ROLA-SIMPLE] ✅ Authentication successful",
