    "id": 62903,
    "text": "Oh, just looking at your PDF now. Don't treat the length component as ASCII - it needs to just be a single byte.\n\nYou're having a 2 byte representation for \"69\" - one byte per character. Whereas you should just have one byte between 0-255. So your hex dump should just be \"45\" - not \"36 39\"",
