    "text": "Thanks for the input. Yes the length is actually variable and and is dynamically calculated based on each applicable message element’s length👍 Do you know if the origin has to tie into the claimed url in the dAppId metadata configuration or the wallet simply doesn’t care and uses the origin sent by the dApp? If it is using the origin to reply then it should be working given that I am getting the wallet responses even though I am using origin ‘http://localhost:5173’?",
