    "text": "There is a few seconds delay between the transaction being accepted by the validators and the gateways seeing it.\n\nI don't think ROLA changes this significantly.\nYou have a proof that the account had the token but if you do something later anything can be changed in between.\n\nIf you want synchronicity you have to pass the proof to a component that does the requested action.",
