    "id": 62798,
    "text": "yeah unfortunately the default package dependencies are broken right now.\nWe talked about it earlier here https://t.me/RadixDevelopers/62308\n\nSo basically best (or at least what worked for me) is to use Rust 1.81, use Cmake < 4.0 (I use the latest 3.31, 4.0 won't work) and set base64ct in Cargo.lock from 1.8.0 to 1.6.0\n\nI use it with this toolchain config\n`\n[toolchain]\nchannel = \"1.81.0\"\ncomponents = []\ntargets = [\"wasm32-unknown-unknown\"]\nprofile = \"default\"`\n\nI hope this helps",
    "date": "2025-11-05T07:43:58.000Z",
