  {
    "id": 62782,
    "text": "I need to update permissions on an existing resource in stokenet via a manifest.\nThe permission I need to set is a complex one: a badge or a specific global caller component is needed.\nAny ideas on how to complete this instruction?\n\n```SET_ROLE\n    Address(\"resource_tdx_2_...\")\n    Enum<ModuleId::Main>()\n    \"non_fungible_data_updater\"\n    Enum<AccessRule::Protected>(\n        Enum<AccessRule::AnyOf>(\n            Array<Enum>(\n                Enum<AccessRuleNode::ProofRule>(\n                    Enum<ProofRule::Require>(\n                        Enum<ResourceOrNonFungible::Resource>(\n                            Address(\"resource_tdx_2_...\")\n                        )\n                    )\n                ),\n                global_caller???```",
    "date": "2025-11-02T08:22:09.000Z",
